[{"Id": 1016980, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "This Istikharah has been reported from Imam Mahdi (a): Write on two pieces of paper: (seeking good from Allah and His Prophet for so and so person (his name) son of so and so lady (his mother s name)) and write on one the pieces of paper: (perform), and on the other piece (do not perform). After preparing them, place both the pieces of paper inside a covering of clay and drop it in water. Then perform Ablution and offer Prayer, then recite the following supplication…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Raqah se istekhaara Hazrat Imam-e-Asr (a) se marwi hai iska tareeqa yeh hai keh; do (2) alag-alag kaghazo’n par likhe’n “KHAIRATOON MENAL-LAAHE WA RASOOLE HI LE-FULA’N IBNE FULAANATE” aur phir ek par likhe’n “AFA’L” (yaani anjaam do) aur dusre par likhe’n “LA-NAFA’L” (yaani anjaam na do) phir un raqawo’n ko matti ki goli ke andar rakh de aur ek aise zarf (bartan) mein daal de jis mein paani ho baad azaa’n wuzu kare 2 rakat namaz padhe aur phir yeh dua padhe…", "UrduDescription": "علامہ حلی نے کتاب مصباح میں کہا ہے کہ اس استخارہ کی آخری حجت کی طرف سے روایت ہوئی ہے اور اس کا طریقہ اس طرح ہے کہ سورہ حمد کو دس دفعہ یا تین دفعہ یا ایک دفعہ پڑھے اس کے بعد سورہ قدر کو بھی دس مرتبہ پڑھے اس کے بعد تین مرتبہ یہ دعا پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicG